Wiz just ro's see if he debuffs then if so just heal till he's oom if not you might arms then wd him and let him die use a nuke if you prefer crispy to slow roasted.<br>
Necro just dispell vs.. Get 80ish pr/dr base and you'll resist CoC and stuff everytime. Bani pet is good to start.<br>
