Kenuon Windrunner <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaeroblaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AeroBLASTER</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/11/01 5:02:39 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> No</span><hr size=1> Root is inefficient.  It is too often resisted and only lasts 20-30 seconds at most.  You would be distracting your attention every 20 seconds to keep him off you.  Better to banish and be done with it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaxercis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Axercis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/12/01 10:43:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: lvl59-60 druid against lvl60 necro, lvl59 wizzie and 59 </span><hr size=1> Root/snare pet will not work against smart pet owners because they will simply dispell their pet. Banishment is high mana cost and all or nothing spell, I'd recommand not using it. Use Blizzard instead. You will take some damage from it also but with good cold resist gear it shouldn't be much and if you do it right pet will be near death after 1 cast, you can then either finish it with dd/root/free dot or just ds yourself and let pet kill itself beating on you.<br>
<br>
Against bard, well, it all depends on how good the bard is. Bard that uses dispell song &gt; druid. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utetriancorbec.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tetrian corbec</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://faceweb-004.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/61/2161961.bmp" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/17/01 2:25:59 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/01/1564901.bmp?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbw?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&fle